The Tennis Court Oath, by Jacques Louis David [1791] (Public Domain Image). Proofs of a Conspiracy by John Robison [1798]

John Robison (1739-1805) was a Scottish scientist, who late in life wrote the one of the definitive studies of the Bavarian Illuminati. He was a contemporary and collaborator with James Watt, with whom he worked on an early steam car, contributor to the 1797 Encylopedia Britannica, professor of philosophy at
